ttp_template:
<group name="bfd_interval_bfd_state_detect_multiplier_local_discr">
Neighbor: {{NEIGHBOR | ORPHRASE}}
 BFD state: {{BFD_STATE | ORPHRASE}}
 Neighbor interface: {{NEIGHBOR_INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}
 Remote discr: {{REMOTE_DISCR | ORPHRASE}}
 BFD interval: {{BFD_INTERVAL | ORPHRASE}} ms
 Detect Multiplier: {{DETECT_MULTIPLIER | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Neighbor: 10.1.1.1
 BFD state: UP
 Neighbor interface: Ethernet1/1
 Local discr: 1
 Remote discr: 100
 BFD interval: 300 ms
 Detect Multiplier: 3

Neighbor: 10.2.2.2
 BFD state: DOWN
 Neighbor interface: Ethernet1/2
 Local discr: 2
 Remote discr: 200
 BFD interval: 500 ms
 Detect Multiplier: 4
textfsm_template:
Value NEIGHBOR (\S+)
Value BFD_STATE (\S+)
Value NEIGHBOR_INTERFACE (.+)
Value LOCAL_DISCR (\d+)
Value REMOTE_DISCR (\d+)
Value BFD_INTERVAL (\d+)
Value DETECT_MULTIPLIER (\d+)

Start
  ^\s*Neighbor:\s+${NEIGHBOR}\s*$$
  ^\s*BFD state:\s+${BFD_STATE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Neighbor interface:\s+${NEIGHBOR_INTERFACE}\s*$$
  ^\s*Local discr:\s+${LOCAL_DISCR}\s*$$
  ^\s*Remote discr:\s+${REMOTE_DISCR}\s*$$
  ^\s*BFD interval:\s+${BFD_INTERVAL}\s+ms\s*$$
  ^\s*Detect Multiplier:\s+${DETECT_MULTIPLIER}\s*$$ -> Record
